---
import FeatureAnimation from "../react/animation/FeatureAnimation.jsx";
---


<section id="features" class="scroll-mt-16 mt-32 mb-48 py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-gray-900 to-black">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 feature-header">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Fitur Unggulan HydroVision</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              Sistem prediksi curah hujan berbasis AI yang dirancang khusus untuk wilayah Gorontalo. Akurat, real-time, dan mudah diintegrasikan.
          </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="card-hover bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-center feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon mx-auto">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 2a10 10 0 100 20 10 10 0 000-20zM12 6v6l4 2" /></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Fokus Wilayah Gorontalo</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Model LSTM dilatih khusus dengan data historis curah hujan Gorontalo selama 5 tahun, menghasilkan prediksi yang relevan dan kontekstual.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card-hover bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-center feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon mx-auto">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16" /></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Evaluasi Model Terbuka</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Tersedia grafik evaluasi akurasi model: perbandingan data aktual vs prediksi, serta visualisasi error dan loss untuk validasi ilmiah.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card-hover bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-center feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon mx-auto">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Prediksi AI Real-time</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Model LSTM kami mampu memproses data secara langsung dan memberikan prediksi curah hujan hingga 3 bulan ke depan.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</section>

<FeatureAnimation client:load />
